    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the overall body of evidence is sufficient to support model use for the stated context of use. Assessed factors demonstrate progressive improvement relative to prior assessment cycles, and Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification provides confidence in the hemolysis index predictions. The team concluded that remaining gaps do not materially affect the regulatory decision.",
